" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但女仔始終係會老既<br />\n如果係全盛時期,真係玩撚哂<br />\n以家都唔弱<br />\n<br />\n再者港女想佢去個級數都仲有距離<br />\n因為佢想食飯就會有10個 8個男仔爭比錢<br />\n直頭唔洗同你&quot;港&quot;<br />\n人地埋單係常識,當然佢有錢自己比,自己屋企都唔係弱<br />\n<br />\n拎港女同佢比,根本就係ON9<br />\n港女臭西扮哂野要R返黎既野,係佢身上係無限咁有人比,唔洗R的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想講句,<br />\n某D巴絲們,你地太年輕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢野既人,會當佢死肥婆行出黎攪攪陣<br />\n知佢野既人,就會明白自己連追佢既條件都未有<br />\n就算係高登仔條件既,係佢眼中都只屬一般<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果自己唔識既就上去GOOGLE<br />\n就如見到巴菲特<br />\n話呢個呀叔有乜巴閉呀,咁多人圍住佢既<br />\n一樣"},{"pid":"7146a173170c0b673d54ae8cd865084ff71f4a0d","tid":85353,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:46:26.000Z","msg":"嘉士伯有冇去?"},{"pid":"ed24ec7dadd675ebf02f3963a876703aa55fe396","tid":85353,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"佢乜水呀"},{"pid":"91318f709afacd48e8262ea5e7cb3a85b47795e6","tid":85353,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢乜水呀</blockquote><br />\n問嘉士柏"},{"pid":"c57a9188fefcf447be6afce22724350a80fc9b3e","tid":85353,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"介紹行程講野慢半拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c83354c812042434cb046904ffdbc046c161e8","tid":85353,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"我　杜如風<br />\n<br />\n 從來都唔自私<br />\n<br />\n今日 嘅午餐 , 就帶大家<br />\n<br />\n嚟到呢間 中外馳名 , <br />\n<br />\n好多港人都慕名而來嘅 - - すき家"},{"pid":"5d1673f8494015194bf696946277c2afbe01f061","tid":85353,"uid":1685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"當年蔡瀾帶團可能都唔駛呢個價<img src