,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T23:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>斷咗條膝頭哥十字韌帶 仲帶到團咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行就行到<br />\n跑的話就話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無啦啦跑咩<br />\n去日本參加運動會咩"},{"pid":"5972c29ea227bb6c83eb98c609e563d2f37733ba","tid":85353,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T23:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三重縣近鐵pass 勁平都冇人去 <br />\n香港有幾多人會行呢條路線...<br />\n睇乜9神宮悶到訓著<br />\n<br />\n二月有雪睇點解唔上白川鄉 上金澤</blockquote><br />\n香港人去到日本度度都話悶又話伏嫁啦叫佢地去齋睇都唔知咩玩法"},{"pid":"ae5bf87dee958464a72e973c09db8e2674281bcb","tid":85353,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三重縣近鐵pass 勁平都冇人去 <br />\n香港有幾多人會行呢條路線...<br />\n睇乜9神宮悶到訓著<br />\n<br />\n二月有雪睇點解唔上白川鄉 上金澤</blockquote><br />\n香港人去到日本度度都話悶又話伏嫁啦叫佢地去齋睇都唔知咩玩法</blockquote><br />\nshopping 咪唔悶<br />\n之前去北九州聽到班香港人話好悶,無野玩<br />\n有心想行嘅大把景點,仲有歷史學<br />\n雖然話去旅行各有喜好,但你去到日本剩係想shopping唔行吓了解當地歷史文化真係好徙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6681e27ab3f7d2c6151510cb445782abfc3e5f0","tid":85353,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三重縣近鐵pass 勁平都冇人去 <br />\n香港有幾多人會行呢條路線...<br />\n睇乜9神宮悶到訓著<br />\n<br />\n二月有雪睇點解唔上白川鄉 上金澤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去完三重<br />\n<br />\n覺得幾正喎<br />\n<br />\n松阪牛好正<br />\n<br />\n鳥羽個水族館勁多野睇<br />\n<br />\n伊勢神宮前條表參道超熱鬧<br />\n<br />\n海女嗰d 都有特色<br />\n<br />\n只係唔需要跟杜如風去<br />\n<br />\n自己去都玩到"},{"pid":"76d71864c4d9f978a208801f16127ad0f2b8282e","tid":85353,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>斷咗條膝頭哥十字韌帶 仲帶到團咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n露下面意思意思jei</blockquote><br />\n露下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49a3806cc3d4db76e3c9df76f1ab3d144f835fa","tid":85353,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:15:08.000Z","msg":"好想同佢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定好撚好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8皮幾野係咪全包呢？係既話其實唔算太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f003a86ba310a48c302c0141f791b1c78585807c","tid":85353,"uid":8269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8132a5980aaaecda1a6fcdb849041d1943fdd0f","tid":85353,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:25:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今日～帶大家黎到！掃貨！</blockquote><br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2f5f90df22f734df6ffb7bf90fb3b4745d586f","tid":85353,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講，杜如風介紹既地方係唔錯</blockquote><br />\n起碼唔係濕鳩旅遊書個d"},{"pid":"594cebdfaf2458663e8a575589f2438f3c6ea91f","tid":85353,"uid":44858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你知道佢既歷史後<br />\n就明白,佢係正宗香港公主<br />\n唔係公主病,而係伸隻手出黎有人埋單<br />\n話今日好悶就會有10個男仔渣車係樓下等<br />\n放工會有仔渣車搶頭淡湯等<br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人都唔知佢乜來頭<br />\n就算80後都未必人人知<br />\n但知道既會覺得佢係好撚傳奇<br />\n根本係公主既教母<br />\n<br />\n如果話佢係港女<br />\n不如話佢係皇帝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但女仔始終係會老既<br />\n如果係全盛時期,真係玩撚哂<br />\n以家都唔弱<br />\n<br />\n再者港女想佢去個級數都仲有距離<br />\n因為佢想食飯就會有10個 8個男仔爭比錢<br />\n直頭唔洗同你&quot;港&quot;<br />\n人地埋單係常識,當然佢有錢自己比,自己屋企都唔係弱<br />\n<br />\n拎港女同佢比,根本就係ON9<br />\n港女臭西扮哂野要R返黎既野,係佢身上係無限咁有人比,唔洗R的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想講句,<br />\n某D巴絲們,你地太年輕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢野既人,會當佢死肥婆行出黎攪攪陣<br />\n知佢野既人,就會明白自己連追佢既條件都未有<br />\n就算係高登仔條件既,係佢眼中都只屬一般<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果自己唔識既就上去GOOGLE<br />\n就如見到巴菲特<br />\n話呢個呀叔有乜巴閉呀,咁多人圍住佢既<br />\n一樣</blockquote><br />\n出現了"},{"pid":"4d34b64ac2099f2689fac4d63ead8de7153e793e","tid":85353,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老實講，杜如風介紹既地方係唔錯</blockquote><br />\n起碼唔係濕鳩旅遊書個d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶本閃閃令就話自己識自由行。"},{"pid":"0cf6d52f2afa0a4425b3053ab9343aa3f5d524d2","tid":85353,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"伸隻手出黎有人埋單<br />\n話今日好悶就會有10個男仔渣車係樓下等<br />\n放工會有仔渣車搶頭淡湯等"},{"pid":"8da3403d65ba0368541d8e2d49472c5cbaa9374e","tid":85353,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:33:29.000Z","msg":"其實幾吸引"},{"pid":"5d0bd2176c307255757f5bf34e25017fdd47a949","tid":85353,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB