 />\n香港人去到日本度度都話悶又話伏嫁啦叫佢地去齋睇都唔知咩玩法</blockquote><br />\nshopping 咪唔悶<br />\n之前去北九州聽到班香港人話好悶,無野玩<br />\n有心想行嘅大把景點,仲有歷史學<br />\n雖然話去旅行各有喜好,但你去到日本剩係想shopping唔行吓了解當地歷史文化真係好徙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕對認同<br />\n去旅行唔係話唔shopping<br />\n只不過去旅行係增廣見聞而唔係側重去shopping"},{"pid":"f71bb7e58444e5496d1ffab581eef4378f2054ac","tid":85353,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話三重縣同伊勢神宮悶果d係咪去開日本淨係鍾意食玩買果d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神宮正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係個度食過杯神作級數嘅豆腐軟雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有條街個氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神宮前條街真係正到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8350304e050b6d36e509a4339b29d038c230a011","tid":85353,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..有人中個頭埋去，我無意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八萬夠我去十次日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4662a04e87e06bfddc70853ca73548a23441e6f","tid":85353,"uid":8271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..有人中個頭埋去，我無意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八萬夠我去十次日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多九萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己去可能仲開心<img src=\"/assets